greyBox is a lightweight jQuery overlay plugin (aka lightbox) which is extensible and easily customizable.
Based on http://jquery.com/demo/grey/

Dependencies:
jQuery fixedBox
  http://www.hovinne.com/blog/index.php/2007/07/30/134-fixedbox-jquery-plugin
  http://github.com/jfhovinne/fixedBox

Usage:

Opens a greyBox on click event:
$('a').greyBox({ width: 760, height: 540 });

Tested with jQuery 1.2.6

